1. *Skidaj* mi muziku sa interneta! (Download the music from the internet for me!)
2. On je često *skidao* kazne za svoje prekršaje. (He often got away with punishments for his offenses.)
3. Ona je *skidala* svoj instalirani program. (She was uninstalling her installed program.)
4. Oni su *skidali* sa njega tužan izraz. (They were taking a sad expression off of him.) 
5. *Skidala* je odeću kako bi se otuširala. (She was taking off her clothes in order to take a shower.)